# Git Hooks

Activate after cloning:

```sh
git config core.hooksPath .githooks
```

## post-checkout

Detects the initial clone (previous HEAD = all zeros) and automatically
compiles `nob.c` then runs `./nob` to produce `odoo-mcp-server`.

Requires: `cc`, `kcgi`, `libtls` (FreeBSD: `pkg install kcgi libressl`)
